[
    {
        "content": "<blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-email=\"brlcad@mac.com\" data-user-id=\"102902\">@Sean</span>  I'm interested in : D) developing a brand new Qt interface<br>\nbut why use Qt? how native Qt Applications look?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-email=\"abdullah.umar.naseef@gmail.com\" data-user-id=\"104241\">@Naseef</span> there's a lot of reasons for using Qt, and it's one of the most popular cross-platform toolkits that provide native platform behavior</p>",
        "id": 121277486,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516385803
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>if you were designing a new application, what would you use?</p>",
        "id": 121277493,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516385827
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>(or migrating a large old application, as in this case)</p>",
        "id": 121277501,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516385841
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Qt is still new to me, I've been doing Gtk and .NET.</p>",
        "id": 121285659,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516398826
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It'll be good to use Qt. ( I googled a bit about this).</p>",
        "id": 121285705,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516398862
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Qt is way better than Gtk and .NET is practically windows-only</p>",
        "id": 121285707,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516398893
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>way better in terms of native behavior at least</p>",
        "id": 121285727,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516398922
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>gtk doesn't try to do that, their model is consistent behavior</p>",
        "id": 121285732,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516398936
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>IMO Archer is already  a really good program.</p>",
        "id": 121285733,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516398936
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Which gui toolkit does it use?</p>",
        "id": 121285744,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516398952
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>it's mediocre from a design perspective ... imho</p>",
        "id": 121285791,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516398973
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>it uses Tk</p>",
        "id": 121285792,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516398980
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and incrTk</p>",
        "id": 121285795,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516398988
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Should we take some widely used cad programs as inspiration?</p>",
        "id": 121285804,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516399051
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Tk is very lightweight</p>",
        "id": 121285810,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516399069
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>We also have to make it start faster, unlike archer.</p>",
        "id": 121285878,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516399151
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>What about some customizable interface?</p>",
        "id": 121285885,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516399191
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Tk is very difficult to make behave exactly like we want, hardly anything is automatic</p>",
        "id": 121285940,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516399210
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Well, A CAD program don't have to be lightweight.</p>",
        "id": 121285950,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516399240
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>it's not \"modern\" by any stretch, and has been complicated over the years to maintain</p>",
        "id": 121285953,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516399246
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>whether the app starts fast or slowly with a loader is on the devs, not the toolkit</p>",
        "id": 121285967,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516399268
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I'm inclined to use the gaming industry as inspiration as they adapt interfaces regularly and must have essential usability</p>",
        "id": 121285979,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516399318
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>that also implies avoiding particular technologies and approaches</p>",
        "id": 121286034,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516399348
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I like Unity3D's customizable interface.</p>",
        "id": 121286037,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516399355
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>(nobody makes games with Tk)</p>",
        "id": 121286038,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516399356
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I did! Some game in Tk when learning python!</p>",
        "id": 121286071,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516399437
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>unity is not open source</p>",
        "id": 121286075,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516399442
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>they have some open source libs they've released, but not the overall framework</p>",
        "id": 121286116,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516399453
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>when I say \"nobody\" I mean no professional shops that ship commercially</p>",
        "id": 121286120,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516399479
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I'm talking about its interface. every part of it is movable. It's just an example.</p>",
        "id": 121286136,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516399513
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Tk runs under a lot of things, so indirectly some use it (e.g., python guis often involve tk), but few directly do any more</p>",
        "id": 121286139,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516399526
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>ahh, sure</p>",
        "id": 121286143,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516399543
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>We can have multiple workspaces.</p>",
        "id": 121286186,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516399565
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>some presets and customizable ones, Like in Blender.</p>",
        "id": 121286195,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516399594
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>sure, that'd be great</p>",
        "id": 121286884,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516400814
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Did you liked it because blender is open source? JK.</p>",
        "id": 121287159,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516401266
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Have you seen a  Qt program that has such interface?</p>",
        "id": 121287172,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516401307
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>their approach actually predates them becoming open source</p>",
        "id": 121287174,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516401308
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>blender uses a custom open gl GUI</p>",
        "id": 121287180,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516401321
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and yes, you can customize an interface like that (or do your own thing in an opengl context</p>",
        "id": 121287186,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516401345
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>they're called qt style sheets: <a href=\"http://thesmithfam.org/blog/2009/09/10/qt-stylesheets-tutorial/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://thesmithfam.org/blog/2009/09/10/qt-stylesheets-tutorial/\">http://thesmithfam.org/blog/2009/09/10/qt-stylesheets-tutorial/</a></p>",
        "id": 121287306,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516401540
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>another: <a href=\"http://discourse.techart.online/t/release-qt-dark-orange-stylesheet/2287\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://discourse.techart.online/t/release-qt-dark-orange-stylesheet/2287\">http://discourse.techart.online/t/release-qt-dark-orange-stylesheet/2287</a></p>",
        "id": 121287321,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516401577
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and <a href=\"http://spinningcubes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/zerobp.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://spinningcubes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/zerobp.png\">http://spinningcubes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/zerobp.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"http://spinningcubes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/zerobp.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://spinningcubes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/zerobp.png\"><img src=\"https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/7d936d6cf75a07f455ede6480fb8f752ff9ce65c/687474703a2f2f7370696e6e696e6763756265732e636f6d2f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f323031342f30352f7a65726f62702e706e67\"></a></div>",
        "id": 121287324,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516401591
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Customizing like moving views, resizing them, make them a separate window. (Like in GIMP)?</p>",
        "id": 121287383,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516401653
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>not about colors or styles, which should be native to operating system.</p>",
        "id": 121287391,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516401678
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>sure you can do that -- that's just basic widget and window management</p>",
        "id": 121287395,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516401686
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>dockable windows/panels</p>",
        "id": 121287396,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516401693
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yeah, I could find a way to say it.</p>",
        "id": 121287399,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516401715
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>multiple layouts.</p>",
        "id": 121287443,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516401750
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>with movable and re-sizable panels</p>",
        "id": 121287447,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516401776
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>yeah, that's pretty fundamental stuff</p>",
        "id": 121287828,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516402549
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>example: <a href=\"https://woboq.com/blog/qdockwidget-changes-in-56.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://woboq.com/blog/qdockwidget-changes-in-56.html\">https://woboq.com/blog/qdockwidget-changes-in-56.html</a></p>",
        "id": 121287829,
        "sender_full_name": "Sean",
        "timestamp": 1516402551
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>That's how BRL-CAD is going to be in the future.</p>",
        "id": 121288231,
        "sender_full_name": "Naseef",
        "timestamp": 1516403205
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-email=\"danielmrossberg@gmail.com\" data-user-id=\"102939\">@Daniel Rossberg</span> <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-email=\"brlcad@mac.com\" data-user-id=\"102902\">@Sean</span> Made a small 2-line patch that changes the layout of CameraView so that it doesn't stretch when the window is vertically resized. What do you think?<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/vAAKnz1LpczYhKlgP765pl3A/qtgui.patch\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"qtgui.patch\">qtgui.patch</a> <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/C6nLKg1djMmQzu20_88lP9el/before.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"before.png\">before.png</a> <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/bgz2DH30fHy7LlsTbl5T25EF/after.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"after.png\">after.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/C6nLKg1djMmQzu20_88lP9el/before.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"before.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/1549/C6nLKg1djMmQzu20_88lP9el/before.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/1549/bgz2DH30fHy7LlsTbl5T25EF/after.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"after.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/1549/bgz2DH30fHy7LlsTbl5T25EF/after.png\"></a></div>",
        "id": 121298975,
